title: Ehime Prefectural Assembly Agrees to Restarting Ikata-3, with Governor to Make Final Decision Soon (JAIF ...
text: ( Source : JAIF - Japan Atomic Industrial Forum Inc) 9 October, 2015 Noriyuki Ishii On October 9, the Ehime Prefectural Assembly held a plenary session to discuss petitions to approve or disapprove restarting the Ikata-3 Nuclear Power Plant
